            "body": "<p>The library must also be sent to <code>java<\/code>:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>java -cp bin:lib/commons-text-1.2.jar MyClass\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>If you're on Windows, you may need to replace <code>:<\/code> with <code>;<\/code><\/p>\n",
